m=divyield;f=calculateyield(dividends:$f64;stockprice:$f64):$f64{let yield=dividends/stockprice;<yield};f=projectincome(yield:$f64;currentyear:$i64;forecastyears:$i64):$f64{let total=mut.0;lp(let i=0;i<forecastyears;i=i+1){let income=yield*(1.0+0.05*i));total=total+income};<total};f=main():$i64{let dividends=10.0;let stockprice=200.0;let yield=calculateyield(dividends;stockprice);let currentyear=2023;let forecastyears=5;let projected=projectincome(yield;currentyear;forecastyears);<0};